# WWE WRESTLEMANIA XL NIGHT 1

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8358659f-714c-43a4-b7e4-6be1ca6e222e/20240406_160315.jpg?format=original)

Wrestlemania kicks off with a brand new WWE introduction video for a brand new era.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/972e046d-ab1b-47df-8209-7c58976147ef/20240406_161203.jpg?format=original)

Triple H opens the show. WELCOME TO A NEW ERA. WELCOME TO WRESTLEMANIA

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8a730173-b0f8-429a-98de-8500ea5ea64d/Screenshot_20240406_161448.jpg?format=original)

## WWE WOMEN'S WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP: RHEA RIPLEY VS BECKY LYNCH

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d7a87d5b-8a37-4f8a-b5dc-819363e01816/Screenshot_20240406_161701.jpg?format=original)

Motionless in White performs Rhea Ripley's theme song for a SICK special live entrance. WWE using some interesting 4K cameras and new graphics tonight for the match introductions.

Great back and forth. Both women looked great. Rhea Ripley putting body scissors on a Texas cloverleaf was awesome. At one point, Rhea sets Becky up for an Electric Chair and then TAKES HER OUTSIDE TO DO IT.

Buckle Bomb Rip Tide and Regular Rip Tide allows Rhea to retain.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7c521d50-5940-406f-8147-a6c7f57372df/20240406_163316.jpg?format=original)

## WINNER: RHEA RIPLEY RETAINS THE WOMEN'S WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/27656918-e631-4b8c-88dc-e0b772cb92b6/20240406_163808.jpg?format=original)

