## **_WINNERS: REY MYSTERIO AND ANDRADE_**

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0564bfe5-9825-4c5f-9394-aaaea821d528/20240406_174054.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_JIMMY USO VS JEY USO_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/21bf2661-a780-43c7-84c0-a37a6f902ea1/20240406_174209.jpg?format=original)

Lil Wayne is here!!!!! Wayne performs A Milli then walks Jey Uso to the ring. Jimmy and Jey Uso do a few spots where they mirror each other, then they sloppily and slowly plot their way to a finish.

## **_WINNER: JEY USO_**

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4af4ae73-08fc-4825-a1b7-955fb5848c56/20240406_180750.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_JADE CARGILL, NAOMI AND BIANCA BELAIR VS DAMAGE CTRL_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/192fe699-fefc-47e1-a2e7-0108835b722f/20240406_180755.jpg?format=original)

Damage CTRL and ‘the Big 3’ make some super impressive entrances. The crowd wants Jade Cargill BAD so there will be a fight to get to this moment. We finally get there and the match ends fairly quickly after

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fd012a29-00ba-4b19-a181-9aac0c192516/20240406_181730.jpg?format=original)

## **_WINNERS: CARGILL, NAOMI AND BIANCA BELAIR_**

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0e0fed81-b6de-4c0d-a4fe-f15f5f5aae1a/20240406_182421.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP: GUNTHER(c) vs SAMI ZAYN_**
    

Sami Zayn tells his family to stay in the back because he doesnt want them seeing him in the ring with GUNTHER. Gable stays in the back and reminds Zayn he will owe him a favor. Sami walks to Gorilla and see Kevin Owens. Owens gives him the support he needed. It’s time.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d14b188f-4f33-460c-8795-8a1e9118a0a1/20240406_182655.jpg?format=original)

MATCH OF THE NIGHT! Sami Zayn gets beat down for 15 minutes before finally channeling the spirit of El Generico in a WWE ring.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b8577152-0ce2-4ffc-b318-b8fe51ecee35/20240406_184730.jpg?format=original)

## WINNER AND NEW INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPION ENDING GUNTHERS 665 DAY REIGN: SAMI ZAYN

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/94212f20-c526-4da6-9977-784310f81752/Screenshot_20240406_190822.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_CODY RHODES AND SETH ROLLINS VS ROMAN REIGNS AND THE ROCK_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d3328917-7280-4cc0-8b60-bdae3fbefdb1/Screenshot_20240406_192435.jpg?format=original)

It’s time for the main event but not after 29 minutes of entrances. Admittedly, the Rock's entrance was absolutely incredible

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4d077451-71f7-44e2-b819-7888d7a0bcd1/Screenshot_20240406_193917.jpg?format=original)

"IF YOU COUNT, YOURE FIRED. I DONT FUCK AROUND”. The Rock has changed the entire game. This is now an Attitude Era esque brawl

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3a9c71ce-eed4-4bda-a30f-22e4c278e420/20240406_200002.jpg?format=original)

The Rock begins an argument with Momma Rhodes but she’s a firecracker. The match continues with Dwayne making sure the ref can never really enforce any rules.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f38090c1-84b6-417d-9256-1fcd6f104b95/20240406_200201.jpg?format=original)

It looks really dire until ROMAN ACCIDENTALLY SPEARS THE ROCK!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8b35d0f1-a343-4ecd-9c66-378aa77ae829/20240406_201032.jpg?format=original)

ITS BLOODLINE RULES

After over 40 minutes, the Rock and Roman Reigns defeat Cody Rhodes and Seth Rollins.

The match ends with Roman having Cody beaten and the Rock asking to tag in and finish him off. Rock pins Cody.

## **_WINNERS: THE BLOODLINE_**

